#Here we provide a demo dataset with KO abundance of 622 paired WGS-amplicon microbiomes
#
#File description
#16s.KO.abd: relative abundance of amplicon microbiomes of 15 paired pairs.
#wgs.KO.abd: relative abundance of WGS microbiomes 15 WGS-amplicon pairs.
#16s.all.KO.abd: relative abundance of all amplicon microbiomes.
#To run the demo, you can either
#
#sh Readme
#
#or
#type the following command
#
#Commands
##Training step
meta-apo-train -t wgs.KO.abd -T 16s.KO.abd -o meta-apo-model.txt

##Calibration step
meta-apo-calibrate -t 16s.all.KO.abd -m meta-apo-model.txt -o meta-apo-calibrated.abd

#Output description
#meta-apo-model.txt: mapping model
#
#meta-apo-calibrated: The calibration file path.
